{"tid":1191762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士佬見人追到站閂門開車係咩心態","createTime":"2019-06-08T05:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:03:20.000Z","uid":185930,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"15b2917d0c0616fc9cbd6528c7773aa871dd8811","tid":1191762,"uid":185930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"明明都到架車隔離，有啲巴士佬急急腳閂門擺出個人生贏家咁嘅樣望住你開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你收工搭車你同事咁對你你點諗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外其實佢飛站遲大到投訴都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過佢飛站搞到半個鐘先有車<br />\n打去投訴話遲啲覆返我，一個月都無回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：廿幾歲人要靠公共交通工具"},{"pid":"2f630acf08ba2da37d789d990d75fa19a3437cff","tid":1191762,"uid":215337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"巴士佬：閂門都要問你？"},{"pid":"0efeb31eeb0f6077c9e6272209a2019429615b9d","tid":1191762,"uid":185930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f630acf08ba2da37d789d990d75fa19a3437cff","tid":1191762,"uid":215337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"巴士佬：閂門都要問你？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"遲到站嗰陣你唔答我？呢啲嘢雙向<br />\n<br />\n問題係喺你隔離你就望住我閂門開車<br />\n你話離遠追唔等就好合理<br />\n我喺正佢隔離"},{"pid":"fd290db25c2f5ae7c2a90b3067a9c02748255d6d","tid":1191762,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"cya nerd"},{"pid":"708173f744c97af7725af52643ec02aacaea07fd","tid":1191762,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"唔係老馮要開比你。"},{"pid":"c8b59dc1562ed0b30569f83551a29fe2a7df24fb","tid":1191762,"uid":185930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"708173f744c97af7725af52643ec02aacaea07fd","tid":1191762,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"唔係老馮要開比你。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"我明佢閂得就唔會開，問題係喺佢隔離佢望住我閂"},{"pid":"48656da09706aae59340f246d2d411fa0973ba7b","tid":1191762,"uid":237922,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"因為開得比你就有第個跟住入<br />\n同地鐵一樣唔會等人上晒車"},{"pid":"4a791917be8c9e28de77dd631949d7f025751709","tid":1191762,"uid":204788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"你有咩問題"},{"pid":"8152a20b04cfd451622b3cb75f022a0acfe4e087","tid":1191762,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a791917be8c9e28de77dd631949d7f025751709","tid":1191762,"uid":204788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"你有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 <br />\n一個鐘"},{"pid":"6f5058611dff90e5a19afdaa352f45e40f00b835","tid":1191762,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8152a20b04cfd451622b3cb75f022a0acfe4e087","tid":1191762,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a791917be8c9e28de77dd631949d7f025751709","tid":1191762,"uid":204788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"你有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 <br />\n一個鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"無野就落車"},{"pid":"be8653929fadfbb4a36966587f70c4fb0e4c6a67","tid":1191762,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"因為會無限loop<br />\n<br />\n同埋你唔知佢等左幾多次你食類情況既人"},{"pid":"a6497811f3216248a97a26c33b8b0960918c02a4","tid":1191762,"uid":125654,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"個個咁樣追法 個個都要等埋 咁咪唔洗開車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等下一班唔洗好耐姐下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6733a